profile.name: 福山 潤
profile.introduction: Jun Fukuyama (福山 潤 Fukuyama Jun, born November 26, 1978) is a Japanese voice actor and singer best known for his roles Lelouch (Code Geass), Koro-sensei (Assassination Classroom), Ichimatsu (Osomatsu-san), Misaki Yata (K), Kimihiro Watanuki (xxxHOLiC), Joker (Persona 5) and several other leading roles.
